text:
Physical education teacher
An unidentified physical education teacher was present at Twin Peaks High School's cheerleading tryouts in March 1989.
Biography
At the tryouts, the teacher was shocked to see the adult Nadine Hurley among the students hoping to be a cheerleader. Nevertheless, she had Nadine perform a tumbling routine. Nadine then performed a corkscrew, throwing a boy across the field.
